# VALUEAGES — Cursor Rules

> These rules apply to all Cursor AI sessions in this repository.

## Project Context

This is a **Next.js 16.2.6** marketing site (Turbopack). It uses React 19, TypeScript 5 (strict), Tailwind CSS v4, and Framer Motion 12.

**IMPORTANT**: Next.js 16 has breaking changes vs. 13/14/15. Do not apply patterns from older Next.js versions. Always read `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` for this version.

## Required Reading

Before any task, read these files:
- `.ai/STACK.md`
- `.ai/ARCHITECTURE.md`  
- `.ai/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`
- `.ai/COMPONENT_RULES.md`
- `.ai/UI_RULES.md`

## Absolute Rules

1. **NO `dark:` Tailwind classes** — dark mode is permanently disabled
2. **Run `npm run build` after every change** — fix all TypeScript errors
3. **All section components** live in `src/components/` (flat, no subdirs)
4. **Default exports only** — `export default function ComponentName()`
5. **Icons**: `lucide-react` exclusively

## Animation Rules

```tsx
// Primary card hover
whileHover={{ y: -6 }}

// Secondary card hover  
whileHover={{ y: -4 }}

// Entrance reveals — always use once:true
initial="hidden" whileInView="visible" viewport={{ once: true, margin: "-100px" }}

// Standard stagger
staggerChildren: 0.08
```

## SVG Gotcha

Always use `gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"` on SVG linearGradients:
```tsx
<linearGradient id="g" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse" x1="0" y1="0" x2="100" y2="0">
```

## Design Tokens

```
brand-teal:  #109B82  (primary)
brand-green: #4F8F7B  (secondary)
brand-rust:  #B85A3A  (warm accent)
brand-tan:   #C99A5A  (warm gradient)
font-serif:  Playfair Display (headings)
font-sans:   Inter (body)
```

## Pre-Commit

- [ ] `npm run build` zero errors
- [ ] No `dark:` classes
- [ ] No `any` types
- [ ] `viewport={{ once: true }}` on all reveals
